original_title: 【健康的な部活っ子限定】部活帰りのウブ女子校生をマ○コばかになるまで突きまくる！強制開発鬼マッサージ。2nd Season
overview: The second unscrupulous massage aimed at school girls on their way home from club activities! Why are you aiming for a club girl? A healthy body trained in club activities has a sensitivity of 120%. If you're going to aim, you don't want to aim for a tuna child. You must see the girls who faint in agony on their way home from school and get squid! Come to think of it, that boyish Kaede-chan who captivated the world's uncles was also a victim...
title: Pounding Innocent Schoolgirls After Club Activities Until They Become Silly! Strong Development Demon Massage. 2nd Season
